My obsession with making abstrktobjkt is an ongoing project in which each piece is grown or is generated manually from the previous, completed artwork. 

Something resonated with me about using these colours together. They seem Right. 

So I found myself working on 4 pieces at once, something I’ve never done before. Each of the 4 here all had the same source.

I just chose a different direction each time I had to make a decision.
